Author: DanishThief
Text: Oof. I have a whole drawer of clothes dedicated to when I get skinny. Most of them came from middle school.

Author: lavendermyth
Text: last month I finally got rid of a pair of jeans that I bought when I was 17 that have literally never fit me, are 9 years out of style, and are clearly women's cut. like there is no universe in which I would ever wear those again but the idiot part of my brain was like 'maybe one day they will fit you.'
